item.title: Are you ready for the adventure of a lifetime?
item.description:
Are you ready for the adventure of a lifetime?

I'm Joel Casey and I'll be your host and guide on this incredible journey of impartial self-awareness, self-discovery, self-realization, self-actualization and self-empowerment!

item.title: Intro to Inward Safari
item.description:
Intro to Inward Safari

The inward Safari gives one the opportunity to get to know ones self. Once you understand why you do what you do, you can change how you experience life. Until you know yourself, you will continue living by default and will feel helpless, hopeless, powerless and victimized- unable to change your life circumstances.
